# Eventfy — Project Deep Dive Summary

## Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TD
    A["React 19 + Vite Frontend"] -->|"api(method, path, body)"| B["FastAPI Backend /v1/*"]
    A -->|"Direct Auth/Realtime"| C["Supabase"]
    B -->|"supabase-py"| C
    C -->|"PostgreSQL 15 + PostGIS"| D["Database"]
    C -->|"Realtime"| E["WebSocket Channels"]
    C -->|"Storage"| F["Buckets: avatars, events, orgs, certs, stories, posts"]
```

---

## Frontend (`frontend/src/`)

### Core Stack
| Package | Version | Purpose |
|---------|---------|---------|
| React | 19.2 | UI framework |
| Vite | 7.3 | Build tool |
| react-router-dom | 7.13 | Routing (createBrowserRouter) |
| framer-motion | 12.34 | Animations & page transitions |
| @tanstack/react-query | 5.90 | Server state (5min stale) |
| @supabase/supabase-js | 2.98 | Auth, realtime, storage |
| lucide-react | 0.577 | Icons |

### Entry Point Chain
`main.jsx` → `StrictMode` → `QueryClientProvider` → `AuthProvider` → `EventStoreProvider` → `App.jsx` → `AppRouter.jsx`

### API Helper (`lib/api.js`)
```javascript
// ✅ Correct usage:
api('GET', '/events/feed')
api('POST', '/events/123/register', { ticket_tier_id: '...' })

// ❌ WRONG (will crash):
api.get('/events/feed')     // TypeError
api('/events/feed')          // Missing method
res.data                     // No .data wrapper — returns parsed JSON directly
```

Also exports `apiUpload(path, file, fieldName)` for file uploads.

### Route Guards ([AuthGuard.jsx](file:///d:/Eventfy-fig/frontend/src/router/guards/AuthGuard.jsx))
| Guard | Behavior |
|-------|----------|
| `AuthGuard` | Requires user + profile. Redirects to `/splash` if no user, `/onboarding/1` (or `/org/setup` for orgs) if `!onboarding_done` |
| `GuestGuard` | Only unauthenticated. Redirects authenticated to `/feed` or onboarding |
| `OrgGuard` | Requires `role === 'organizer'`. Redirects non-orgs to `/feed` |
| `AdminGuard` | Requires `role` in `['local_admin', 'global_admin']` |

### Context Providers
- **AuthContext**: `user`, `profile`, `loading`, `supabase`, `signOut()`, `refreshProfile()`
- **EventStore**: Reducer-based store for `registeredEvents`, `savedEvents`, `followedOrgs`, `feedScrollY` with optimistic operations

