### Screens (25 folders, 35+ routes)
All screens in `screens/` — each folder has `.jsx` + `.css`. Key screens: Feed, Explore, EventDetail (polymorphic by type), Chat/ChatHub, PlayerProfile, OrgProfile, CreateEvent, CommandCenter, AdminPanel, 6 onboarding steps, 4 auth screens.

---

## Backend (`eventfy-backend/`)

### Stack
FastAPI + supabase-py + python-jose (JWT) + Pillow

### Router Prefixes
| Router | Prefix | Key Endpoints |
|--------|--------|--------------|
| auth | `/v1/auth` | `/me`, login, register |
| users | `/v1/users` | profile CRUD |
| events | `/v1/events` | `/feed`, `/{id}`, `/create`, `/{id}/register` |
| organizations | `/v1/orgs` | org CRUD, followers |
| registrations | `/v1/registrations` | event registration |
| volunteers | `/v1/volunteers` | apply, approve |
| teams | `/v1/teams` | team CRUD |
| qr | `/v1/qr` | generate/validate tokens |
| chat | `/v1/chat` | channels, messages |
| stories | `/v1/stories` | story CRUD |
| notifications | `/v1/notifications` | CRUD, mark read |
| gamification | `/v1/gamification` | XP, badges, scoreboard |
| posts | `/v1/posts` | org announcements |
| admin | `/v1/admin` | org approval, user mgmt |
| search | `/v1/search` | unified search |
| sponsorships | `/v1/sponsorships` | sponsor management |

### Critical First-3 Endpoints
1. `GET /v1/events/feed` — paginated feed with scope filter + registered IDs
2. `GET /v1/events/{id}` — full event detail + polymorphic type data
3. `GET /v1/auth/me` — user profile + badges + skills + managed orgs

---

## Database Schema (23+ tables)

Core: `profiles`, `organizations`, `org_members`, `org_followers`, `events`

Type-specific: `event_sport_details`, `event_science_details`, `event_charity_details`, `event_cultural_details`, `event_speakers`, `event_performers`, `event_ticket_tiers`, `event_doi_links`

Registration: `event_registrations`, `volunteer_roles`, `volunteer_applications`, `teams`, `team_members`

Social: `chat_channels`, `messages`, `message_reactions`, `polls`, `poll_votes`, `stories`, `story_frames`, `story_views`, `connections`, `notifications`, `posts`

Gamification: `badges`, `user_badges`, `xp_transactions`, `skills`, `user_skills`, `certificates`

Other: `qr_tokens`, `sponsorships`, `golden_tickets`

